TaxJar,provides,retailers,with,easy,access,to,the,information,they,need,to,file,their,sales,tax,returns,for,all,counties,and,cities,in,the,U,S,TaxJar,provides,access,to,its,information,through,two,APIs,the,Smart,Sales,Tax,API,and,the,Sales,Tax,Rate,API,The,Smart,Sales,Tax,API,allows,users,to,determine,the,amount,of,sales,tax,that,should,be,withheld,based,on,a,shipment,s,origin,and,destination,points,The,Sales,Tax,Rate,API,allows,users,to,retrieve,the,sales,tax,rate,for,a,given,location